      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This example has been fastidiously maintained with the critical Vanos system serviced and the rear subframe reinforced for structural integrity. It retains its factory variable M differential lock and offers immediate throttle response and balanced chassis dynamics. The suspension remains taut, providing excellent lateral grip and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. A true driver\u2019s car in solid condition, ready for the track or the canyon roads.",
